feat: iOS SwiftUI app - Authentication & Dashboard

Native iOS app with SwiftUI + complete backend integration:

FEATURES:
✅ Authentication (Login & Register)
✅ Dashboard with full statistics
✅ API Service layer with auto token refresh
✅ Theme system (colors, typography)
✅ ViewModels with async/await

SCREENS:
- LoginView - Email/password auth with validation
- RegisterView - Full registration form
- DashboardView - Complete stats overview

DASHBOARD STATS:
- Properties, Clients, Activities, Deals count
- Total Revenue & Commission
- This month revenue
- Recent activities feed
- Today's schedule & overdue items

API INTEGRATION:
- Full URLSession networking
- Token storage with UserDefaults
- Auto token refresh on 401
- All backend endpoints connected

PROJECT STRUCTURE:
- Models/ - Codable data models
- Views/ - SwiftUI screens
- ViewModels/ - Business logic
- Services/ - API service
- Utils/ - Theme & extensions

TECH STACK:
- SwiftUI (declarative UI)
- Async/Await (modern concurrency)
- Combine (reactive)
- URLSession (networking)

Ready to build in Xcode!

